<p><span class="section-subtitle">Things that I use. Last updated on 7th September, 2017</span></p>

<p>I am frequently asked about my setup, the hardware and software I use for my work, or what kind of equipment one should choose. Since I don‚Äôt always have the opportunity to give an answer as precise as I would like, I thought a page describing the setup I am using could be a good idea. Listed here are the Hardware, Cameraware, Software and Paintware that I use.</p>

